    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered icon. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and proactive rod bearing replacement. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally sound with documented subframe reinforcement. Every mechanical component, from the individual throttle bodies to the suspension bushings, remains in peak factory specification. Finished in a flawless deep gloss with an interior free of bolster wear, this is a turn-key machine for the discerning driver.",
