      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage. This car is in showroom condition, featuring a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish and professional ceramic coating; you will find no rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections on any panel. The interior is equally pristine, with the premium leather upholstery remaining matte and supple, completely free of bolster wear or creasing. It still retains that signature new-car scent. Every technological feature and electronic component operates with factory-level precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive service history performed exclusively at the original dealership. It comes complete with both sets of keys, all original manuals, and custom-fitted floor mats. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the finest example on the market.",
