    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. This example is mechanically impeccable, having undergone proactive rod bearing replacement and complete rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity. The Double VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the 6-speed Getrag manual transmission shifts with factory-spec precision. Power is managed via the M Variable Differential Lock, providing exceptional lateral grip. With zero fluid seepage, a pristine undercarriage, and a flawless compression profile across all six cylinders, this M3 delivers a pure, analog performance profile that remains uncompromised.",
